=> the app which is runs at contianer and to run outisde browser for access that is prt mapping ..
                 ** PORT MAPPING **
docker run -it -p 8000:3000 test-image 
                 local :container port 

=> adding Environment Varible in run time 
-  docker run -e PORT=8000 -p 8000:8000 my app

              ## how to push custom image on Docker Hub ##
=> docker push username/image-name
1. docker login
2. docker build -t username/image-name .
3. docker push username/image-name
4. docker run -it -e PORT=7000 -p 7000:7000 test-image


# DOCKER COMPOSE
=> when we run two container on differen two images ,docker compose help us to run multiple container .
=> docker compose is a tool used to run multiple docker containers together using one file and one command .
1.firstly ,first write in docker compose file .
then run docker compose up or docker compose down
docker compose up --build 
docker compose down

# docker networking : 1. bridge 2. host 3. none 
=> docker network ls
=> docker network inspect bridge
=> docker network inspect host

# custom network :
=> docker network create name








# docker volumes 
=> wehn we stop container , we use docker volumes
=> docker volumes store data permantly outside containers so data remains safe even if continers are delted or restarted ..


                 
